title: 3BR - 4BR 2bath Historic Brownstone, nr MedCenter and NorthCentral U
posting_body: ['Classic original 1902 brownstone, one of only a few remaining.', 'With natural maple floors and amazing original oak millwork.', 'Thick tall natural oak doors with 9-10 foot ceilings, all with a new kitchen.', 'On the east edge of downtown about a mile from the UofM West Bank.', 'This is a very unique and special architectural gem for that special person;', 'One who can appreciate a bygone era of stone and wood craftsmanship.', 'All within walking/biking/lyfting to downtown and the UofM, off-street parking available.', 'Caretaker position available for experienced cleaner/handy person, email your resume.', 'Deposit, background check and references required.']
